{"tid":1824351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有關[有限度人傳人]","createTime":"2020-01-14T11:16:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T12:17:50.000Z","uid":147010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6599f6463575d0632a28e7fa5659e984351da2f1","tid":1824351,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:16:21.000Z","msg":"睇返之前嘅中東呼吸綜合症MERS<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vPjDBAp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvPjDBAp.png&h=6806cc09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKeywords: 免疫力低，屬高危<br />\n<br />\nH7N9<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/14/185823_14b4f30fb889da8cd7baa85898eb1f9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F14%2F185823_14b4f30fb889da8cd7baa85898eb1f9a.png&h=1497b9a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上都出現過有限度人傳人呢個term<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇返wiki解釋(我知唔係100%啱)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P8w6Luq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP8w6Luq.png&h=9c175087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKeywords:與病患有非常密切的接觸<br />\n<br />\n再補充一下 H7N9有關有限度人傳人嘅文章<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JR7d9Wz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJR7d9Wz.png&h=ed8221b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKeywords: 通過密切接觸有效地在雪紹中傳播，並可以出現有限度的空氣飛沫傳播<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4bn503V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4bn503V.png&h=80aec45a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張係啱啱嘅，佢後面補充左主要喺小型群體出現。<br />\n<br />\n總結:雖然都係唔撚清唔撚楚，不過我估所謂有限度人傳人係指有緊密嘅接觸。相對地冇咁容易傳染。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌你班高層，可唔可以解釋清楚啲</span><br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正"},{"pid":"429f87217527a317f8ce30765d351391e80d848d","tid":1824351,"uid":108347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:17:16.000Z","msg":"剩係武漢同香港人會中，仲唔係有限度人傳人?"},{"pid":"50c10f5f3f1014c46e85084ba0b441f8763dcf75","tid":182